Fourthstone Opportunity Fund LP  Financing
Fourthstone Opportunity Fund LP just submitted form D announcing  Indefinite financing.  Fourthstone Opportunity Fund LP was able to sell $3,170,048. The total private offering amount was Indefinite. The financing was made by 9 investors. Minimal accepted investment was $1,000,000. The financing document was filed on 2014-12-16. Fourthstone Opportunity Fund LP is based in  13492 CLAYTON ROAD  ST. LOUIS 63131. The firm's business is Pooled Investment Fund. The form was signed by  N/A Fourthstone LLC.





